text: René Mioch at the International Film Festival Rotterdam in 2016 René Mioch in 1992 René Mioch (born in Waalwijk, March 6, 1959) is a Dutch journalist and presenter for radio and television. He currently presents Film RTL (RTL), DVD Today (Net 5) and Ambilight Opening Night (RTL). He has had several minor film roles, mainly as cameos of himself, including appearances in Loverboy and Too Fat Too Furious. In 2006, he was elected as a member of the International Academy of Television Arts and Sciences. == External sources == * ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch radio personalities Category:Dutch television presenters Category:People from Waalwijk
